{"tid":1462813,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"機場一定要繼續搞！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:43:26.000Z","uid":73959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f825916011aca5e463587c9b460e54265d2f44","tid":1462813,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:22:21.000Z","msg":"但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搞不等如阻旅客上機</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n0813機場即時檢討!! 應該用JAM 唔應該用BLOCK!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462309</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個巴打講嘅JAM法非常好 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場一定要繼續搞！<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以日日搞</span><br />\n因為我哋都要俾旅客返屋企<br />\n如果用<span style=\"color: gold;\">阻</span>人上機/登機 輿論會變差<br />\n記唔記得琴日點解就咁坐三個鐘都有成效？<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人多</span></span><br />\n今日就係因為人少 所以現場先決定要阻<br />\n<br />\n仲未明我講咩？<br />\n<br />\n我總結你聽：<br />\n<br />\n不能夠日日搞機場 -&gt; 人數一定唔夠<br />\n要搞一定要擇日 -&gt; 儲人數<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">人數夠 -&gt; 不必阻！坐喺度已經夠癱瘓到</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c843f7579ae891856ccff4b9aa0f51721a2a0170","tid":1462813,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"塞旅客的話，留返一個counter出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。"}]}